No functions named merge, clean, or auto_fix are allowed.

## 10. Sample Data Requirements
Use 10-row CSV with: 2 clean records, 3 email typos, 2 invalid emails, 1 missing phone, 1 high amount, 1 duplicate pair. After upload, zero changes to raw_rows. All issues appear as pending suggestions.

